data.description: Assumable VA Loan- 2.75% Rate! We welcome offers from non veterans. Charming single-story home on a generous corner lot! This inviting residence offers a convenient RV gate & parking area complemented by a spacious 2-car garage. Discover an open layout featuring wood-look tile flooring & gorgeous light fixtures accentuating the neutral palette. The open-concept kitchen showcases granite counters, generous cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, & an island w/additional prep space & breakfast bar. Split main suite has a private bathroom boasting dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Fantastic backyard is a blank canvas awaiting your landscaping ideas; take a moment to relax on the covered patio as you envision the countless memories waiting to be created in this delightful home. You won't be disappointed.
